  "reference_number": "RUS2294",
  "remarks": "\nANO DIALOG is an involved entity under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because it is or has been involved in:  obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia, through 1) carrying on business as a Government of Russia-affiliated entity, and; 2) carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance, namely, the Russian information, communications and digital technologies sector.\n",
